Some questions/comments:

1. Why doesn't this Action use the TimeSelection type?

2. What is the difference between affordance = undefined and affordance = TimeSelectionAffordance.NONE and affordance just isn't specified (there are three ways to basically ignore affordance)? Would be nice to tighten this up so only one or two of those is possible.

